OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FThe first ever secure school for young
OL,7,Foffenders will soon open in Rochester,
OL,8,FKent.
OL,10,FIt's called Oasis Restore and aims to
OL,11,Fgive girls and boys, aged between 12
OL,12,Fto 18, intensive education and
OL,13,Ftraining.
OL,15,FIt's a much smaller setting than a
OL,16,Fyoung offenders institution (YOI) or
OL,17,Fprison and will provide specialised
OL,18,Feducation and training.
OL,20,FIt's part of measures to reduce re-
OL,21,Foffending by children.
