OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FHow will it work?
OL,8,FThe school will be run by education
OL,9,Fprovider Oasis Restore rather than the
OL,10,FPrison Service, and inside it will be
OL,11,Flaid out like a school inside the
OL,12,Fprison walls.
OL,14,FIt will be home to up to 49 children
OL,15,Fat any one time ` both boys and girls.
