OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FStaff will be trained to offer a broad
OL,7,Fcurriculum and offer one-to-one
OL,8,Flearning support, and they will set
OL,9,Fchallenging targets in core academic
OL,10,Fsubjects such as English and
OL,11,Fmathematics.
OL,13,FOfsted inspectors will hold the
OL,14,Festablishment to the same standards as
OL,15,Fall other schools nationwide `
OL,16,Fensuring the education on offer is of
OL,17,Fthe best possible standard.
