OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FDespite an 82% drop in the number of
OL,7,Fyoung offenders in youth custody since
OL,8,F2010, the few hundred children left
OL,9,Fhave complex needs.
OL,11,FThey have often committed serious
OL,12,Foffences and have serious mental
OL,13,Fhealth problems and poor education.
OL,15,FThe aim of Oasis Restore Secure School
OL,16,Fis to put education and healthcare at
OL,17,Fthe heart of steering young offenders
OL,18,Faway from gangs and knife crime.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
