OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FThe design is based on international
OL,7,Fresearch which shows that smaller
OL,8,Fsettings, high-quality education and
OL,9,Fhealthcare, plus a specialised
OL,10,Fworkforce of teachers and youth
OL,11,Fworkers are the key to successfully
OL,12,Fturning the lives of young people in
OL,13,Fcustody around.
OL,15,FHow do they differ from 'regular'
OL,16,Fschools?
OL,18,FPlacement decisions will be made
OL,19,Finternally by the Youth Custody
OL,20,FService (YCS).
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
