OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FChildren and parents will not be able
OL,7,Fto apply for placement in a secure
OL,8,Fschool rather than a YOI.
OL,10,FYoung people will be supervised by
OL,11,Fhighly trained staff and the secure
OL,12,Fsite has the same rigorous security
OL,13,Fprocedures as other custodial settings
OL,14,Ffor children.
