OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FThe rooms in the school are fitted
OL,7,Fwith the latest secure in-room
OL,8,Ftechnology which will allow children
OL,9,Fto continue homework and projects in
OL,10,Ftheir rooms and contact their families
OL,11,Fto maintain crucial ties that are
OL,12,Fproven to cut reoffending.
OL,14,FIs the secure school only for children
OL,15,Ffrom Kent?
OL,17,FNo, the secure school is not only for
OL,18,Fchildren from Kent.
