OL,3,CSecure Schools: What are they and how
OL,4,Cdo they differ from 'regular' schools?
OL,6,FChildren sentenced to custody could be
OL,7,Fplaced there from anywhere in the
OL,8,Fcountry.
OL,10,FCloseness to home is considered
OL,11,Falongside a number of other factors in
OL,12,Fdetermining where a child is placed.
OL,14,FThe YCS placements team will decide
OL,15,Fwhere to place each child sentenced or
OL,16,Fremanded to custody, according to the
OL,17,Fchild's individual needs and
OL,18,Fcircumstances.
